message.text:
𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑯𝑼𝑵𝑻 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒌𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑪𝒐𝒎𝒎𝒊𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒆 ☁️🎈

Our deepest gratitude to the TamHunt 2025 working committee for making this event a soaring success! Together, we flew higher than Pampanga’s hot air balloons, the very inspiration behind our theme. 🪂🍃

You turned TamHunt into an unforgettable sky-high moment. With every ounce of effort and passion, we didn’t just reach the skies… we broke through them. ✨☝️

Palaging 𝑪𝒀𝑪𝒊𝒃𝒐𝒍 sa 𝐡𝐢𝐦𝐏𝐀𝐌𝐏𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐝—hanggang sa muli! 🌟

Maraming salamat, Y'ers! 💫

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption by Stephanie Ashley Buenaventura 
Publication Materials by Janelle Tañedo, LJ Rocha, and Shanley Gungon

𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑯𝑼𝑵𝑻 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒌𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑪𝒐𝒎𝒎𝒊𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒆 ☁️🎈

Our deepest gratitude to the TamHunt 2025 working committee for making this event a soaring success! Together, we flew higher than Pampanga’s hot air balloons, the very inspiration behind our theme. 🪂🍃

You turned TamHunt into an unforgettable sky-high moment. With every ounce of effort and passion, we didn’t just reach the skies… we broke through them. ✨☝️

Maraming salamat, Y'ers! 💫

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Publication Materials by Janelle Tañedo, LJ Rocha, and Shanley Gungon
